{"tid":2237252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被取消註冊教師手寫感言感謝市民關心和支持","createTime":"2020-10-10T06:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T06:10:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c36e25e1c97b90173a327f96df7d22aefc0e998","tid":2237252,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553967-20201010.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553967-20201010.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=33e57b00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553967-20201010.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=400fc3da\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553967-20201010.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n教協在社交網站上載九龍塘宣道小學被取消註冊教師的手寫感言，表示感謝市民關心、支持和鼓勵，稱留言及打氣都是守護香港教育界最重要的支柱。<br />\n<br />\n有關教師早前被指有計劃地散播港獨，被教育局以嚴重專業失德為由，取消教師註冊。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄今早在本台節目說，教師要為教材負責，質疑該名教師是否明白港獨在香港憲制地位的不可行性。"},{"pid":"6e7bf62efcbf8da93eb5105fe92da96ef4d171c5","tid":2237252,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"老師保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}